com.fasterxml.transistore.basic

Class BasicTSKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.EntryKey
      • com.fasterxml.transistore.basic.BasicTSKey

  • public class BasicTSKey
extends com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.EntryKey
    Value class that contains identifier used for accessing piece of content: basically contains optional partition id and String.
